commit.message:
Rename wordlping to synthetic monitoring (#46)

* Rename go module to github.com/grafana/synthetic-monitoring-agent
* Rename pkg/pb/worldping to pkg/pb/synthetic_monitoring
* Change metrics namespace from worldping_bbe_sidecar to sm_agent
* Change strings from "worldping" to "synthetic-monitoring"
* Change info metric name to sm_check_info
* Change reported agent string
* Change worldpingTLSConfigToBBE to smTLSConfigToBBE
* Rename binaries
* Rename worldping to synthetic monitoring in packaging scripts
* Change worldping to synthetic-monitoring in docker files
* Remove "worldping" from Makefile
* Update README.md
Signed-off-by: Marcelo E. Magallon <marcelo.magallon@grafana.com>

* add pprof
* update diagram in README
* add all commandline args in config and pass to command at startup
Co-authored-by: woodsaj <awoods@grafana.com>
